  <p>
    <span class="mark" aria-hidden="true">✦</span>
    Gabriel Miro — Senior Full-Stack Engineer
  </p>
  <p class="quiet">
    <a href="mailto:gabriel.34.miro@gmail.com">gabriel.34.miro@gmail.com</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel-miro-972b1a2b3"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
    >
      LinkedIn
    </a>
    <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
    <span>© {year} — hand-built with Astro, React, GSAP, and PIXI</span>
